// Dragnet [Container]: dragnet-container-2024-0494 — Vulnerable Base Image Pull
// Status: deprecated | Level: critical | ID: a62925ac-cc67-595d-a419-9d695302b6f6

any where
  (process.executable like~ "*chainguard:*" or process.executable like~ "*debian:10*" or process.executable like~ "*debian:12*" or process.executable like~ "*debian:13*" or process.executable like~ "*debian:14*" or process.executable like~ "*wolfi:*")
